summary: Adds some lighting to breezehome. I know that avenicci gives it light, this adds even more.
descriptionHtml: I added the lighting because I thought it looked dark and scary, now when you walk through your home you feel welcome in every room. If you see floating candles it\'s because you haven\'t upgraded breezeholme yet. Send me a message on Skyrim nexus or leave a comment and I will try to fix it for you. Trust me, after you upgrade breezeholme through avenicci this mod will look perfect. If it doesn\'t, message me at the Skyrim nexus Forums or leave a comment on this mod please.
author: Unreliablebob
